    "Id": "mechdef_ferdelance_FDL-3",
    "Name": "Fer-de-Lance FDL-3",
    "Details": "Created during the heyday of the Star League era, the Fer-de-Lance is a 30 ton Cannopian BattleMech built by Majesty Metals and Manufacturing at their Canopus IV facilities. Surviving the succession wars mostly intact, the Fer-de-Lance is still produced in small quantities by MMM every year and features in most MAF light mech lances. The FDL-3 is built around a 240 rated XL engine and an endosteel skeleton. Outfitted to hunt enemy battle armor, the FDL-3 boasts a pair of Streak SRM-2s, a pair of Small Pulse Lasers and a pair of Medium Pulse Lasers. A head mounted machine gun and dhs round out the design.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Nimble</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.99</color></b>",
    "Icon": "uixTxrIcon_spider"
  },
